Statute.Title: National Housing Strategy Act
Statute.OtherLangTitle: (Stratégie nationale sur le logement, Loi sur la)

CIF.Text: CIF 2024, c. 15, s. 339 comes into force on the second anniversary of the day on which the Fall Economic Statement Implementation Act, 2023 receives royal assent or on an earlier day to be fixed by order of the Governor in Council see s. 341(1) — Not in force
